        Selling in a Rising Brisbane Market vs a Falling Market: Strategy Differences
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        The same property in the same suburb can require a completely different selling strategy depending on whether the market is rising, stable, or softening. Here is how the playbook changes.
      </p>
